Testing the Reservations API
How can I make test reservations?
You can try out our tutorial to create a test reservation.

What are the reservation details I need to show to properties in my system?
You need to show the following reservation details in your system to the properties:

Booking.com reservation ID
Reservation status
Time stamps of reservation creation and latest change
Booker details: name, alias email address, phone number, Genius status
Guest names
Number of guests, and a breakdown by number of adults and children
Room name and room type ID (RoomTypeCode in OTA and room>id in BXML)
Rate name and rate ID, including meal plan and cancellation policy
Promotions applied
Rate-rewriting
Add-ons booked by the guest
Check-in and check-out date
Price per room night
Additional taxes and fees
Total price including all taxes and fees
Smoking preference
Additional information and special requests made by the guest
Credit card data (in a PCI-compliant format)
